front.title: Bantha
front.gametext: May carry 2 passengers. Bantha ability = 1/2. May move as a 'react' only to a battle or Force drain (if within range). Each Tusken Raider at same exterior site is power +1.
front.lore: Transport, pack animal. Many breeds of different sizes and colors. Three meters tall. Can go weeks without food or water. Found throughout the galaxy.
